data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value: -------------------------------------- My_EventBot Hayatta Kal---------------------------------------------------- declare @CharN16 varchar(64) = (select Charname16 from SRO_VT_SHARD.._Char where CharID = @CharID) if(@EventID = 6 and exists (Select CharName16 from My_EventBot.._HayattaKal_List where CharName16 = @CharN16))begin update My_EventBot.._HayattaKal_List set Durum = 'DC' where CharName16=@CharN16 END if(@EventID =9 or @EventID=11 and exists (Select CharName16 from My_EventBot.._HayattaKal_List where CharName16 = @CharN16) and (select ItemID from SRO_VT_SHARD.._Inventory where Slot =8 and CharID = @CharID) != 0 )begin update My_EventBot.._HayattaKal_List set Durum = 'INJOB' where CharName16=@CharN16 end if(@EventID = '20') begin DECLARE @kesenCharName VARCHAR(512) = @Desc SELECT @kesenCharName = REPLACE(@kesenCharName, LEFT(@kesenCharName, CHARINDEX('(', @kesenCharName)), '') SELECT @kesenCharName = REPLACE(@kesenCharName, RIGHT(@kesenCharName, CHARINDEX(')', REVERSE(@kesenCharName))), '') -- Hayatta_Kal Etkinlii. if(@Desc like '%no job, Murderer, no freebattle team%' and exists(select CharName from My_EventBot.._Hayatta_Kal)) begin update My_EventBot.._Hayatta_Kal set Durum = 'ld' where CharName=@CharN16 Update My_EventBot.._Hayatta_Kal set Toplam_ldrme = Toplam_ldrme+1 where CharName = @kesenCharName end end -------------------------------------- My_EventBot Hayatta Kal----------------------------------------------------

data.name: richTextBox2.Text
data.value: -------------------------------------- My_EventBot PLUS Log---------------------------------------------------- if (@Operation = 90 OR @Operation = 160) begin declare @len_desc1 int set @len_desc1 = CHARINDEX (']',@strDesc) declare @CharmyEventBot varchar(50) select @CharmyEventBot = CharName16 from SRO_VT_SHARD.._Char WHERE CharID = @CharID declare @baslan_plus varchar(250) if(@len_desc1 = 9) begin set @strDesc = SUBSTRING(@strDesc,0,9) set @baslan_plus = SUBSTRING(@strDesc, 8, 1) end else if(@len_desc1 = 10 ) begin set @strDesc = SUBSTRING(@strDesc,0,10) set @baslan_plus = SUBSTRING(@strDesc, 8, 2)end if(@baslan_plus >= 0 and @ItemRefID = 24178 or @ItemRefID = 24196 or @ItemRefID = 24202) -- begin insert My_EventBot.._PlusLog(CharID,CharName16,ItemID,ItemSerial64,Plus,Tarih,Durum) values(@CharID,@CharmyEventBot,@ItemRefID,@ItemSerial,@baslan_plus,GetDate(),0)end end -------------------------------------- My_EventBot PLUS Log----------------------------------------------------
